<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 1 (Kyle) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リアラ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Reala</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kyle</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあカイルは
十年以上先の未来からやってきたというの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So you came here from ten years in the future?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>う〜ん。
そういう事になるみたいだね。
難しい話はよくわかんないけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeahhhh. That seems to be what's going on.
I don't really get stuff that's tough to
understand, though.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>きっと運命ね。
カイルがここに来てくれた事は</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It must be fate that you came here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>少なくともわたしは
来てくれたのがカイルでよかったと思ってる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At the very least, I'm grateful you're here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わたしの事
人形じゃないって言ってくれて嬉しかったわ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I was happy to hear you say I'm not just some doll.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なに言ってるのさ。
そんなのあたりまえだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you talking about?
Isn't that just obvious?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……うん。
それが当たり前に言えるからこそ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Yeah. If nothing else, it's BECAUSE
you can say it like it's so obvious.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイル、あなたはわたしの英雄ね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kyle, you are my hero.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
